V45: path: deposit() → principalStETH += arithmetic | guard: none on overflow but Solidity 0.8.24 auto-checks | verdict: DROP (FP gate 3: Solidity >=0.8 protects)

V52: path: deposit() → safeTransferFrom / withdrawPrincipal() → safeTransfer / agentWithdraw() → safeTransfer | guard: nonReentrant + state updated before transfer | verdict: DROP (FP gate 3: CEI followed, nonReentrant)

V54: path: exit() uses balanceOf(this) | guard: none on force-feed | verdict: CONFIRM [85] - exit() bypasses principalStETH accounting by reading raw balance

V55: path: _getCurrentRate() → ORACLE.latestRoundData() | guard: oracle is wstETH/stETH not derivative | verdict: DROP (FP gate 1: correct feed for asset)

V69: path: _getCurrentRate() → latestRoundData | guard: checks answer > 0, staleness, but missing answeredInRound >= roundId | verdict: CONFIRM [95]

V70: path: agentWithdraw() → lastAgentWithdrawal = uint32(block.timestamp) | guard: none on overflow | verdict: CONFIRM [100]

V73: path: all transfers use SafeERC20 | guard: SafeERC20.safeTransferFrom measures balance diff | verdict: DROP (FP gate 3: SafeERC20 handles fee-on-transfer)

V77: path: deposit() has no cooldown reset for agent | guard: agentWithdraw has separate cooldown per agent wallet | verdict: DROP (FP gate 1: no deposit-based cooldown reset mechanism)

V79: no tx.origin used | verdict: DROP

V80: SafeERC20 used throughout | verdict: DROP

V82: path: agentWithdraw() cooldown check | guard: require(block.timestamp >= lastAgentWithdrawal + withdrawalFrequency) | verdict: DROP (FP gate 3: proper guard)

